    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it spotless and garage-kept, so it\u2019s basically perfect inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly pampered, this is the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
