    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, retaining its deep, factory luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and protected with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition, with the premium leather seating showing zero bolster wear and all interior surfaces remaining free of scratches or sun fading. Every electronic component, from the advanced infotainment system to the precision climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by factory-certified technicians. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. Included in the sale are all original keys, the factory owner\u2019s manual, and a comprehensive binder of service records. For the discerning buyer seeking perfection, this is the finest example currently available on the market.",
